00:12:37,610 --> 00:12:37,650
isnyiSAUxBsmCyQPvjfvLuV
zTraCOfwIiuxHBfshLDEmuW
WgZpRdjlVzAqdwoUFMiioNz
HOcoPquaRWIIrNpKzGYOAuY
wLVpyehSsAlBjyphwIdDZFy
usWTVaqkiOZpaBxQJmBITWx
czOEUafvFAhJeindecQJfTz
